title: Looking for casual, friendly club with lots of people
body: I'd love to enter a club which is a casual, friendly club with a high population. I had an account a year ago that was level 30. Thank you. {{sticker:slayer-jinx-catface}}

replies.body: My club Skinz is growing in numbers, but not really an active club.. i Have it for club tag.
hey just added you on league, lookin for a group of social players to group with and hav a laugh (usually at myself) :p
